---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome!</h1>
			<p>
				Welcome to the official <a href="https://raceplay.site/">Raceplay.site</a> Content Page
			</p>
			<p>
				You will have received a downloadable PDF file from the purchase.<br>
				We call it a token.<br>
				Always refer to that token.
				Though the site is ever changing. We also encourage you to not leak any of the content. the website almost shut down due to compromise of that degree, please be empathetic to the cause, we never wanted to switch to Pay-Per VIew, but we had too to keep everything flowing, but gladly we are back to subscription based, meaning you see the Entire library! for $20-$30 a month. We appreciate you guys keeping the vision alive.
			</p>
			<p>
				Our main social medias are <a href="https://twitter.com/RaceplayVideos"
					>Twitter
				</a> and <a href="https://t.me/RaceplayClips">join us on Telegram</a> to ask questions.
				<br>
				*WE ARE UPDATING LOGIN SYSTEM SO IF YOU HAVE PURCHASED WITHIN THE LAST MONTH AND STILL HAVE A VALID 1 MONTH ACTIVE, YOU MAY REQUEST ACCESS.
			</p>
			<div>
			<!--login section start-->
			<script type="text/javascript" src="https://identity.netlify.com/v1/netlify-identity-widget.js"></script>
		</head>
		<body>
		  <!-- Add a menu:
		   Log in / Sign up - when the user is not logged in
		   Username / Log out - when the user is logged in
		  -->
		  <div data-netlify-identity-menu></div>
		  <p>
			Before requesting drive access make sure the email you request matches the one you sign up with.
		  </p>
		
		  <!-- Add a simpler button:
			Simple button that will open the modal.
		  -->
		  <div data-netlify-identity-button>Login/Sign Up</div>
		</div>
		  <!--login section clip -->
			<a class="read_more" onclick="toggleReadMore()" href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1h64kYBJy8IGwYuSH86dd5VhkXvlz1Tm-?usp=sharing">Drive</a>
			
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
